{"tid":1657911,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"呢排咁緊張 講個笑話比大家聽","createTime":"2019-10-16T09:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T03:17:07.000Z","uid":38779,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9d0edc8931348eab94214d338db691b7854ec4","tid":1657911,"uid":38779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"全民口罩月 哈哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n緊急法（禁蒙面法）一推<br />\n大家就話要反抗呀 繼續戴呀<br />\n諗埋真係驚既就戴個普通外科口罩 減低風險<br />\n<br />\n但去到今時今日 出街得返一到兩成人戴<br />\n戴住口罩既人彷彿成為異類<br />\n我明白各有各做 但希望大家唔好變得善忘<br />\n<br />\n美國戰線係有進展 但都唔好過份依賴<br />\n而且仲未完全通過 除左兩院通過投票<br />\n仲要協議內容 仲要過埋侵侵（除非兩院都有2/3既贊成）<br />\n成日話自己香港自己救 自己都要繼續努力先係架嘛<br />\n唔存在階段性勝利架<br />\n大家都要一齊堅持落去"},{"pid":"552f3e2deb9d582bd270ed3411b1ce2c7d52125b","tid":1657911,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:59:31.000Z","msg":"幫我推多次上熱門!<br />\n1020 見!<br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去[2]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657270</a>"},{"pid":"04c2349703cdf2c6d85be984e81483d09fc41e91","tid":1657911,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9c79b98480f1f81cbccd3141acc331d61dc8660e","tid":1657911,"uid":38779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:07:57.000Z","msg":"唉屌 唔記得左<br />\n10月20號 九龍見 <br />\n希望大家唔好遲（太多）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b1d937ded0ce86b609a33fd9417e7e4bf9d31e","tid":1657911,"uid":144156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"一到兩成 好似講多左<br />\n唔係返到大學 都冇見過人戴"},{"pid":"0c624877df924533a2c5e7fb1c0ef39c9bd85afc","tid":1657911,"uid":138420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:12